/*
Argument 0: Background
Argument 1-2: X and Y
Argument 3-4: X scale and Y scale (0 to 1280)
Argument 5-6: Offset Horizontal and Vertical (uses fa variables)
Argument 7-8: View Width and Height
Argument 9: Lock
Argument 10-11: Tile X and Y
*/
draw_background_tiled_ext_scr(argument0,argument1,argument2,argument3,argument4,0,c_white,1,argument5,argument6,argument7,argument8,argument9,argument10,argument11);